{"tid":855471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【施政報告】每所「國家重點實驗室」及「國家工程技術中心香港分中心」的每年資助提高至1000萬元。","createTime":"2018-10-10T05:19:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T05:25:57.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fe8ed5624f29c9b1ded10979a5ab9364905d2521","tid":855471,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20181010/s00010/9bf42508af15ac97cae3784df5f632ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20181010%2Fs00010%2F9bf42508af15ac97cae3784df5f632ba.jpg&h=ade3d3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今日發表任內第二份《施政報告》，針對創科界發展，繼今年度財政預算案預留的500億元外，政府將再投放280億元在大學研究、再工業化、公共服務應用科技和加強創科氛圍等工作。<br />\n<br />\n政府將向研究資助局「研究基金」注資200億元，加強大學的研究實力，以及建議成立30億元「研究配對補助金計劃」，增加研究撥款來源。此外，政府亦擬推出「傑出學者計劃」，壯大本地科研和創科人才。<br />\n<br />\n為加速再工業化，政府建議成立20億元「再工業化資助計劃」，資助生產商在港設立智能生產線，並計劃撥款20億元在工業邨為先進製造業建設所需生產設施。<br />\n<br />\n另外，為釋放香港的科研力量， 創新及科技基金目前資助的三項有關計劃的撥款將增加一倍，即每所大學的技術轉移處每年可獲得的資助由現時最多400萬元增加至最多800萬元；「大學科技初創企業資助計劃」對的資助上限提高至每年800萬元；以及每所「國家重點實驗室」及「國家工程技術中心香港分中心」的每年資助提高至1000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1539148468262&amp;issue=20181010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1539148468262%26issue%3D20181010&d=VvRda%2FphPWYygqpmMXAMCXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=390c69fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1539148468262%26issue%3D20181010&h=8e560805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1539148468262&amp;issue=20181010</a>"},{"pid":"9dfa87c2dcf4eaa5524811e78517c39354b60731","tid":855471,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賣港"},{"pid":"fcd1a08fce93939131efc636ef608478c295a360","tid":855471,"uid":61853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:23:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"9db508f8a79b9ff5244260a0080f40e7e3b3a513","tid":855471,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:24:45.000Z","msg":"［值得聽］王凱峰：浸會炒人為咗'百人大計'谷研究 傳政府將'南水北調' 用過百億喺深圳搞科研中心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/854798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/854798</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b1cfeda7ff307f71c897d3f85d0204020079d7e7","tid":855471,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e716e3a80c2136e7de6c38828801ad4cdb59f47","tid":855471,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"香港繼續做白手套<br />\n做到爛為止"}]}